name: Wooof
Lore: 'Kadas''sa''Nikto. One of Jabba''s best pilots. Often pilots Jabba''s space yacht. Smuggler. Prefers to be flying combat starfighters.',
Text: 'Deploys only at Tatooine. Power +2 when defending a battle at a Jabba''s Palace site. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if piloting an [Independent Starship] starship or if Jabba is aboard).',
